Azure offers services for Artificial Intelligence (AI), Machine Learning (ML), and IoT/Edge computing.

AI Services:

* Vision
* Speech
* Language

ML Services:

* Model training
* Deployment
* MLOps

IoT/Edge Services:

* IoT Hub
* IoT Central
* Azure IoT Edge

For example, AI services can analyze images, ML can predict trends, and IoT can manage connected devices.

# Real-Life Use Case:
A real-life use case is smart factories using IoT sensors and ML analytics.

# Real-Life Example:
Another example is healthcare diagnostics using AI image recognition.

These services enable intelligent, connected systems.
